  <entry>
    <title>数论</title>
    <link href="/2020/02/08/%E6%95%B0%E8%AE%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/"/>
    <url>/2020/02/08/%E6%95%B0%E8%AE%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#algorithm</p><h3 id="数论基础">数论基础</h3><p>We have <span class="math inline">\(a^2+b^2=3025\)</span>,what's thevalue of <span class="math inline">\(a+b\)</span> ?</p><p>sssss test</p><h4 id="相关定理">1 相关定理</h4><h5 id="fermat小定理">1.1 Fermat小定理</h5><p><span class="math inline">\(p\)</span> 为质数，若 <spanclass="math inline">\((a,p)=1\)</span>，则 <spanclass="math inline">\(a^{p-1}\equiv1(mod\ p)\)</span>。</p><h5 id="euler定理">1.2 Euler定理</h5><p>若 <span class="math inline">\((a,p)=1\)</span>，则<spanclass="math inline">\(a^{\varphi(p)-1}\equiv1(mod\ p)\)</span>，其中<span class="math inline">\(\varphi(p)\)</span> 为Euler函数。</p><h5 id="斐蜀定理">1.3 斐蜀定理</h5><p>任意整数 <span class="math inline">\(a,b\)</span> ，存在整数 <spanclass="math inline">\(x,y\)</span> ，满足<spanclass="math inline">\(ax+by=(a,b)\)</span>。</p><p><span class="math inline">\(proof:\)</span> 当 <spanclass="math inline">\(b=0\)</span> 时 <spanclass="math inline">\((a,b)=a\)</span> 。当 <spanclass="math inline">\(b\neq0\)</span>时，假设<spanclass="math inline">\((x,y) \rightarrow (a,b)\)</span> ，<spanclass="math inline">\((x_1,y_1) \rightarrow (b,a \% b)\)</span>，可以得到 <span class="math inline">\((x,y)\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\((x_1,y_1)\)</span> 之间的关系。由欧几里得算法可知<span class="math inline">\((a,b)=(b, a\ \% \ b) =...=(x,0)\)</span>只需求得每一相邻层的 <span class="math inline">\(x,y\)</span>关系通过递归即可得逆推得到 <span class="math inline">\((x,y)\)</span> 。<span class="math inline">\(ax+by=(a,b)=bx_1+(a-b*\left \lfloor\frac{a}{b} \right \rfloor )y_1=ay_1+b(x_1-\left \lfloor \frac{a}{b}\right \rfloor y_1)\)</span> ,故有 <span class="math inline">\(x=y_1,y=x_1-\left \lfloor \frac{a}{b} \right \rfloor y_1\)</span></p><p>往往会把斐蜀定理运用在扩展欧几里得算法中，既求出 <spanclass="math inline">\(x\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(y\)</span> ，又求出 <spanclass="math inline">\((a,b)\)</span> 。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">exgcd</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;x, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> &amp;y)</span> </span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(!b) &#123;<br>x = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, y = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> d = <span class="hljs-built_in">exgcd</span>(b, a % b, y, x);   <span class="hljs-comment">// 换y与x的位置 简化更新x y的过程</span><br>y = y - (a / b) * x;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> d;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对于一般的方程<span class="math inline">\(ax+by=c\)</span>，当且仅当<span class="math inline">\(d|c\)</span> 才有解，可以先求出一组 <spanclass="math inline">\(ax+by=d\)</span> 的特解 <spanclass="math inline">\(x_0,y_0\)</span> 再乘上 <spanclass="math inline">\(\frac{c}{d}\)</span>即为一般方程的特解。事实上其通解可表示为 <spanclass="math inline">\(x=\frac{c}{d}x_0+k\frac{b}{d}\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(y=\frac{c}{d}y_0-k\frac{a}{d}\)</span> 其中 <spanclass="math inline">\(k\in Z\)</span> 。</p><h4 id="乘法逆元">3 乘法逆元</h4><p><span class="math inline">\(x / a \equiv x * b (mod\ m)\)</span> 则称<span class="math inline">\(b\)</span> 为 <spanclass="math inline">\(a\)</span> 的模 <spanclass="math inline">\(m\)</span> 的乘法逆元。可以进一步转化为 <spanclass="math inline">\(ab\equiv 1(mod\ m)\)</span></p><p><span class="math inline">\(a\)</span> 存在乘法逆元的充要条件是 <spanclass="math inline">\(a\)</span> 与 <spanclass="math inline">\(m\)</span> 互质。</p><p>当 <span class="math inline">\(m\)</span> 为质数时由<strong>Fermat小定理</strong>得乘法逆元 <spanclass="math inline">\(b=a^{m-2}\)</span>。<spanclass="math inline">\(a^{m-2}\)</span> 可能很大，可以模 <spanclass="math inline">\(m\)</span> ，因此可以利用快速幂 <spanclass="math inline">\(qmi(a, m-2, m)\)</span> 求得逆元。</p><p>当 <span class="math inline">\(m\)</span> 为合数时由<strong>Euler定理</strong>可得 <spanclass="math inline">\(b=a^{\varphi(m)-2}\)</span>。也可以通过扩展欧几里得算法<span class="math inline">\(ax+py=1\)</span> 求得 <spanclass="math inline">\(x\)</span> ，显然 <spanclass="math inline">\(ax\equiv1(mod\ p)\)</span> 成立，故 <spanclass="math inline">\(x\)</span> 即为逆元。</p><h4 id="组合数">组合数</h4><p>一、用数组存阶乘和阶乘的逆元 求多个模p的组合数 <spanclass="math inline">\(factor[k]\equiv k!\ (mod\ p)\)</span> <spanclass="math inline">\(infactor[k]\equiv k!\)</span> 的逆元<spanclass="math inline">\(\ (mod \ p)\)</span></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++">factor[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i ++) &#123;<br>factor[i] = factor[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * i % p;<br>infactor[i] = infactor[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * <span class="hljs-built_in">qmi</span>(i, p - <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, p) % p;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">C</span>(a, b) = (<span class="hljs-number">1ll</span> * factor[a] * infactor[a - b] % p * infactor[b] % p + p) % p;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>二、只求某一个组合数模p的值</p><p><span class="math inline">\(Lucas\)</span> 定理：<spanclass="math inline">\(C_a^b\equiv C_{a\ mod \ p}^{b\ mod \p}*C_{a/p}^{b/p}(mod \ p)\)</span></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-comment">// a,b在int范围内时</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">// a,b一定要小于p</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">C</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> b, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> p)</span> </span>&#123;            <br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, j = a; i &lt;= b; i ++, j -- ) &#123;<br>res = <span class="hljs-number">1ll</span> * res * <span class="hljs-built_in">qmi</span>(i, p - <span class="hljs-number">2</span>, p) % p;<br>res = <span class="hljs-number">1ll</span> * res * j % p;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> res % p;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// a,b &gt; 2e9 lucas定理</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">lucas</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> a, <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> b, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> p)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(a &lt; p &amp;&amp; b &lt; p) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">C</span>(a, b, p);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-number">1ll</span> * <span class="hljs-built_in">lucas</span>(a / p, b / p, p) * <span class="hljs-built_in">C</span>(a % p, b % p, p) % p;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>三、求原组合数（无模p）</p><p>先筛质数，再根据<spanclass="math inline">\(C_a^b=\frac{a!}{b!(a-b)!}=p_1^{\alpha_1}p_2^{\alpha_2}...p_k^{\alpha_k}\)</span>分解质因数，再利用高精度乘法 其中 <spanclass="math inline">\(a!\)</span> 中的 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_i\)</span> 的个数 <spanclass="math inline">\(\alpha_i\)</span> = <spanclass="math inline">\(\left \lfloor \frac{a}{p_i} \right \rfloor+\left\lfloor \frac{a}{p_i^2} \right \rfloor+...\)</span> (数据过强可以用<span class="math inline">\(LL\)</span> 压 <spanclass="math inline">\(9\)</span> 位）</p><h4 id="卡特兰数">卡特兰数</h4><p><span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> ，它们将按照某种顺序排成 <spanclass="math inline">\(2n\)</span> 的序列，形成的序列中满足任意前缀序列中<span class="math inline">\(0\)</span> 的个数不小于 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 的个数的序列有多少种</p><p>假设序列不满足该条件，那么存在一个最小的 <spanclass="math inline">\(p\)</span> 使得前 <spanclass="math inline">\(2p+1\)</span> 个数中有 <spanclass="math inline">\(p\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(p+1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> ，将后面的<spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 取反，那么之后还剩下 <spanclass="math inline">\(n-p\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(n-p-1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> ，即得到了一个有 <spanclass="math inline">\(n+1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(n-1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 的序列。相反的，有 <spanclass="math inline">\(n+1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(n-1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 的序列也一定存在一个最小的 <spanclass="math inline">\(p\)</span> 使得前 <spanclass="math inline">\(2p+1\)</span> 个数中有 <spanclass="math inline">\(p\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(p+1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 即不满足条件的序列与有 <spanclass="math inline">\(n+1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(n-1\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 的序列形成一个双射。因此答案为 <spanclass="math inline">\(C_{2n}^{n}-C_{2n}^{n+1}=\frac{C_{2n}^{n}}{n+1}\)</span>。我们称这个数为卡特兰数。</p><p>拓展：</p><ol type="1"><li><span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个左括号和 <spanclass="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个右括号组成的合法序列数为 <spanclass="math inline">\(Cat_n\)</span></li><li><span class="math inline">\(1,2,...,n\)</span>经过栈，形成的合法出栈序列数为 <spanclass="math inline">\(Cat_n\)</span></li><li><span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个节点构成的不同二叉树数量为<span class="math inline">\(Cat_n\)</span></li><li><span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 和 <spanclass="math inline">\(m\)</span> 个 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> ，<spanclass="math inline">\(0\)</span> 的个数不小于 <spanclass="math inline">\(1\)</span> 的个数的序列数为<spanclass="math inline">\(C_{m+n}^{n}-C_{m+n}^{n+1}\)</span><br /></li><li>从 <span class="math inline">\((0,0)\)</span> 到 <spanclass="math inline">\((n,n)\)</span> ，只能向上或者向右且不能碰到 <spanclass="math inline">\(y=x\)</span> 的走法数为 <spanclass="math inline">\(2Cat_{n-1}\)</span></li></ol><p><a href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/1318/">有趣的数列</a>性质满足从 <span class="math inline">\(1\)</span> 开始往 <spanclass="math inline">\(2n\)</span> 填，奇数项数始终不小于偶数项</p><p><a href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/1319/">树屋阶梯</a>阶梯拼积木 满足 <spanclass="math inline">\(f[n]=\sum_{i=0}^{n-1}f[i]f[n-1-i]\)</span></p><p><a href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/1317/">网格</a>卡特兰数 <span class="math inline">\(n,m\)</span> 的情形 对应拓展4</p><p><a href="https://www.acwing.com/problem/content/1317/">概率论</a> 求<span class="math inline">\(n\)</span>个结点的二叉树叶子节点数的期望</p><p>设 <span class="math inline">\(g[n]\;\)</span> 为<spanclass="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个结点的二叉树叶子节点数的总和，$ f[n]$为 <span class="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个结点的二叉树的个数（即 <spanclass="math inline">\(Cat_n\)</span> )，则期望 <spanclass="math inline">\(E=\sum N_ip_i\)</span> 其中 <spanclass="math inline">\(p_i=\frac{1}{f[n]}\)</span> 因此目标为 <spanclass="math inline">\(E=\sum N_ip_i=\frac{g[n]}{f[n]}\)</span> 即求<span class="math inline">\(n\)</span>个结点的二叉树叶子节点数的总和，对于任意一个 <spanclass="math inline">\(n-1\)</span> 个结点的二叉树有 <spanclass="math inline">\(n\)</span> 个位置可以添加叶子，因此 <spanclass="math inline">\(g[n]=f[n-1]*n\)</span> 。</p>]]></content>
    
    
